<h2>

  <a name="uebertragung"></a>




    Which transmission rate do I need in order to view / listen to the interviews?

  </h2>



<p>To play the videos in high quality, a broadband internet connection (2000 kbit/s, a DSL 2000 internet connection) is
  recommended. If less bandwidth is available, the low transmission rate may cause you to experience problems displaying
  the videos.</p>







