<h2>

  <a name="wechsel-qualitaeten"></a>



    Why does the video interview continue to play in some browsers when switching between qualities?

  </h2>



<p>When switching between video qualities, Internet Explorer 7 will not automatically stop playing. You must stop the
  video before you change the quality. </p>
<p>In other browsers, playback will be stopped automatically when switching between video qualities (e.g. Firefox).</p>

