  <a name="bildershow"></a>



    How do I navigate the photo gallery?

  </h2>



<p>Navigate the photo gallery by moving the mouse over the two arrow buttons left and right in the display window (the
  symbols &lt; and &gt;).</p>
<p>You can close the photo gallery with the exit symbol <strong>X</strong> in the lower right.</p>

